TITLE=Current version of hot cocoa recipe
DATE=2009-12-17 19:22:05
POSTID=876
CATEGORIES=food;

*   4 teaspoons cocoa
*   4 packets splenda
*   1/6 teaspoon cornstarch (helps thicken the cocoa suspension)
*   1 pinch salt
*   1 cup boiling water
*   Add milk or cream for additional calories
